name: Tamamo no Mae (Fate Extra)
description:
My Lora model for Tamamo no Mae from Fate Extra. Most of the preview images were made with weight 0.8.

You can outfit your waifu fox lady in few ways with this model:

  • Usual outfit - tamamo no mae, japanese clothes, blue thighhighs, short kimono, blue bow, sash, fox tail, geta

  • 3rd ascension FGO outfit - tamamo no mae, japanese clothes, blue bow, kimono, very long hair, multiple tails, wide sleeves, off shoulder, hair ornament, bell

  • Gothic style "Sable Mage" - tamamo no mae, fox tail, mini top hat, black thighhighs, black footwear, frills, hair ribbon, black dress, shorts

  • Summer bikini - tamamo no mae, blue bikini, fox tail, straw hat, wet shirt, sandals, scarf, bracelet

  • Casual CCC outfit - tamamo no mae, fox tail, black thighhighs, pink bra, striped hoodie, open hoodie, necklace, black footwear, black shorts, hair scrunchie

Tips and tricks:

  • Ascension outfit has a long kimono that will often cover legs, but you can add blue thighhighs, geta from regular outfit.

  • multiple tales doesn't work so well, better put extra weight on it.

  • I took care to tag fox shadow puppet that she does with her hands so that works (about as well as hands usually do)
